Package com.skobbler.ngx.navigation

Contains classes needed for making a turn by turn navigation.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    SKNavigationListener
    Listener for the callbacks related to navigation received from the ngx map library
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SKAdvisorSettings
    Stores information about the audio advisor settings, that will be used during a navigation.
    SKCrossingDescriptor
    Class that contains information about how to generate visual advice images.
    SKNavigationManager
    Class which handles all the navigation methods.
    SKNavigationSettings
    SKNavigationSettings defines settings for turn by turn navigation.
    SKNavigationState
    Class used in navigation for updating the route state.
    SKVisualAdviceColor
    The SKVisualAdviceColor is used to store the colors of a generated visual advice image.
    SKZoomLevelConfiguration
    SKZoomLevelConfiguration stores information about the speed interval for a zoom level that will be used during navigation.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    SKAdvisorSettings.SKAdvisorLanguage
    Languages supported by the advisor.
    SKAdvisorSettings.SKAdvisorType
    Type of audio advisor.
    SKNavigationSettings.SKNavigationMode
    Defines types of navigation.
    SKNavigationSettings.SKNavigationType
    Navigation types
    SKNavigationState.SKStreetType
    Specifies type of street.
